{"tid":2443583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<反對泰> 梁君彥：相信議會仍會有不同政治理念的人士","createTime":"2021-03-12T06:56:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T07:43:02.000Z","uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b8b452bf7f03e5116033622e42adfb5a84b80e86","tid":2443583,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:56:32.000Z","msg":"梁君彥相信議會仍會有不同政治理念人士<br />\n<br />\n立法會主席梁君彥對人大通過相關決定，表示尊重和支持，希望人大常委會完成相關修訂工作後，特區行政機關盡快將本地立法的草案提交立法會審議，使相關選舉在未來12個月能有序舉行，並做好解說工作。<br />\n他相信理順憲制秩序後，議會仍會有不同政治理念的人士或政黨，繼續反映香港的整體利益，履行監察政府的憲制職能，為香港市民謀求福祉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2382544\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2382544&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=880842e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2382544</a>"},{"pid":"7d5e33631e1af4061859cdcabff8d459aeb5212f","tid":2443583,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b49a55360368a768caddb53abb420446151582","tid":2443583,"uid":179409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:59:11.000Z","msg":"個制度改到甩皮甩骨仲話「監察政府」<br />\n真係當人傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd07cad1dda9f52b67733051ad4b932a25f3b6a","tid":2443583,"uid":45934,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:59:20.000Z","msg":"當然可以揀<br />\n有吞精<br />\n有中出<br />\n有屌屎忽<br />\n有顏射<br />\n<br />\n但冇得揀唔唔屌"},{"pid":"7006d9151fe767a94434f2045c5b1c1b3c730216","tid":2443583,"uid":224533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:59:44.000Z","msg":"紫荊黨，民賤聯，工賊會<br />\n<br />\n黑 紅 深藍 淺藍 偽黃"},{"pid":"d40f87e00932905609786be5461c140b2a391d28","tid":2443583,"uid"